  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400f.",
    "Slice the bread into 1-inch thick slices and place on a baking sheet.",
    "Bake the bread in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile, mix together the cashew cheese, lemon juice, olive oil, garlic powder, and salt in a small bowl.",
    "Remove the bread from the oven and brush the cheese mixture onto each slice.",
    "Place a slice of bread on each bamboo skewer.",
    "Drizzle the honey over the bread and sprinkle with flaky sea salt.",
    "Place the skewers on a bamboo tray and bake in the oven for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and sprinkle with fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
